thread.title_full: Better Music reviewed by Ocean Grove customer

author: Ocean Grove customer
title: Ocean Grove customer
text:
Great knowledge of product and also accessories I needed. Obvious first hand experience and knowledge of products and answered all my technical questions.
Product was dispatched within hours of my online order and arrived smack on time. Product was well packed and looked handled well.
All good!
